dc_description_s: This polygon data layer represents recreation areas for the City of Madison, Wisconsin in 2016. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Madison_City_Recreation_2016.gdb. The features included in this geodatabase are Botanical_Gardens, City_Maintained_Bike_and_Walk_Paths, Golf_Courses, Mall_Concourse, and Zoo.
